Type: Package
Package: sdarr
Title: Slope Determination by Analysis of Residuals
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Robert", "Wendlandt", , "robert.wendlandt@uksh.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6368-1622")),
    person("UKSH", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Slope Determination by Analysis of Residuals (SDAR) for
    automated and objective linear-fitting of mechanical test-data (see:
    standard ASTM E3076-18 <doi:10.1520/E3076-18> or a detailed
    description in E. Lucon (2019) <doi:10.6028/NIST.TN.2050>). As the
    SDAR-algorithm heavily uses linear regressions, a faster version is
    additionally available to find the optimum region for the final
    linear regression by random sub-sampling within the normalized range
    of the test-data.
